Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo! My sweet Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweet smell of the red flowers\Nis calling to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go near the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't meet Hotaruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was the scent of the flowers\Nthat did that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:02:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh gods that shake free\Nthe craggy seats of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Hiruko afloat in the wooden\Ncatalpa boat to the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And let her drift to the land\Nof Mizuho Ashihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Till she arrives at\Nthe foot of the crag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2... 3... 4... 5...\N6... 7... 8... 9... 10...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus is the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wavering, wavering...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The dead will be brought to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to pray, Bungo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What, to a god I don't\Nbelieve in anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't believe in anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you upset Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cruel, Hotaruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Ruka's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone finds us in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare she spoil the end of our\Nimportant purification ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because Ruka's\Nbecome so close to Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to need to be punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do it again, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease me... I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
