Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the same place\Nas the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have been so\Nneglectful recently.
