Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be having\Na good time with my father, Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief Priest started it, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you've gotta keep nice\Nand close so it doesn't fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, it looks like Ruka\Nhas a low tolerance for pain.
