Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem close with Ryo, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A servant scheming to work with Ryo\Nand the Kizuki family lineage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That calls for harsh punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Noisy wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body is going to aid\Nthe god Hiruko too, Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please! The Chief Priest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can be recognized\Nas a descendent of Hiruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ryo?
