Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that all a dream last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat, Miss Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka, isn't this hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My family is greatly indebted\Nto the Kizuki family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When I leave this island,\Ncome with me.
