Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to me!\NNobody but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate when you're like that!
