Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bungo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Use me?
