Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In place of Junko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like with Itsuki.\NIt was the same that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You want Kasumi to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, we need a replacement.
